mixin book-slide-item(img, heading, desc)
  .book-item__slider-wrapper
    .book-item__wrapper
      .book-item
        .book-item__image-wrapper
          img(src=img).book-item__image
        .book-item__content
          .book-item__heading=heading
          .book-item__desc=desc
          a(href="#" role="button").btn.book-item__btn Подробнее

